snippet.title: Flight 74 | Launch Trailer | Meta Quest Platform
snippet.description:
Flight 74 is a unique story based flight game exclusively for the Meta Quest.
Your plane has experienced engine trouble and you’re forced to land at a seemingly deserted runway in the distance. Unfortunately for you, the airstrip is owned by the Cartel.  

Now available for Meta Quest! 
https://metaque.st/3AJk4BM
